---

## âœ… Recap: How to Kill the Ghost

### âŒ Don't do this:

```ts
{ params }: { params: { id: string } }
```

### âœ… Do this:

```ts
{ params }: { params: Promise<{ id: string }> }
const { id } = await params;
```

This fixes `.next/types/...` ghost errors **in both route handlers and layouts**.

